{"tid":1321475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[斷捨離老師] 失戀應該掟咩好","createTime":"2019-07-15T16:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:01:05.000Z","uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"465504e150077d9905e47bd56e393fd2288f5c5a","tid":1321475,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:25:36.000Z","msg":"電視機　電腦　　廚具　衣物&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n失戀青年全屋物件掟落街<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天水圍天悅出現高空擲物狂徒，一名青年疑受失戀打擊精神大受刺激，昨日瘋狂地將屋內的家具、電器及雜物等掟落街中，警方接報封鎖現場，與擲物狂徒對峙期間，他仍不停拋下大小物件，最後屋內除重型電器及床外，幾乎全被他拋清光，幸而未有傷及途人。事件擾攘兩個多小時後，警方破門入屋將狂徒制服送院，他涉嫌高空擲物被扣查。　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050328/Article_news/28la2p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050328%2FArticle_news%2F28la2p3.jpg&h=4dc2e11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p11.jpg&h=05aa471e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青年疑失戀，不停將屋內電器及雜物擲落街上，警方將現場封鎖，地上滿布被擲下的家具及雜物。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p133.jpg&h=ec6ddf85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青年所住單位事發後空空如也，只剩下幾件大型家具及電器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p16.jpg&h=0f6f4e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被男事主擲下的一張床褥，從三十六樓飛下街中。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050327/Article_news/27la2p14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050327%2FArticle_news%2F27la2p14.jpg&h=4d4a497a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發狂擲物落街的男事主，不時在屋內大聲呼叫。"},{"pid":"fe5615c408e775574c55381027171dc498e72fe7","tid":1321475,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"掟煲"},{"pid":"4b8520c9bd65a32e46753d346de95b07ee0cd985","tid":1321475,"uid":259362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />癡線"},{"pid":"1ccb3d62408b9954ae471f9a505f75ddb693db50","tid":1321475,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9e3d08dddd576b767c7711c66b46eabaeed28f","tid":1321475,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"又失戀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}